#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:1 of
msgid "Compute the qr factorization of a matrix."
msgstr "计算矩阵的 QR 分解。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:3 of
msgid ""
"Factor the matrix `a` as *qr*, where `q` is orthonormal and `r` is upper-"
"triangular."
msgstr "将矩阵 `a` 分解为 *qr*，其中 `q` 是正交矩阵，`r` 是上三角矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:6 of
msgid "Matrix to be factored."
msgstr "待分解的矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:8 of
msgid ""
"method to calculate qr factorization, tsqr as default  TSQR is presented "
"in:      A. Benson, D. Gleich, and J. Demmel.     Direct QR "
"factorizations for tall-and-skinny matrices in     MapReduce "
"architectures.     IEEE International Conference on Big Data, 2013.     "
"http://arxiv.org/abs/1301.1071  FSQR is a QR decomposition for fat and "
"short matrix:     A = [A1, A2, A3, ...], A1 may be decomposed as A1 = Q1 "
"* R1,     for A = Q * R, Q = Q1, R = [R1, R2, R3, ...] where A2 = Q1 * "
"R2, A3 = Q1 * R3, ..."
msgstr ""
"计算 QR 分解的方法，默认为 tsqr。TSQR 参见：A. Benson, D. Gleich, 和 J. "
"Demmel. Direct QR factorizations for tall-and-skinny matrices in "
"MapReduce architectures. IEEE International Conference on Big Data, 2013."
" http://arxiv.org/abs/1301.1071。FSQR 是适用于宽而矮矩阵的 QR 分解：A = ["
"A1, A2, A3, ...]，A1 可分解为 A1 = Q1 * R1，对于 A = Q * R，Q = Q1，R = ["
"R1, R2, R3, ...]，其中 A2 = Q1 * R2，A3 = Q1 * R3，..."

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:8 of
msgid "method to calculate qr factorization, tsqr as default"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:10 of
msgid "TSQR is presented in:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:12 of
msgid ""
"A. Benson, D. Gleich, and J. Demmel. Direct QR factorizations for tall-"
"and-skinny matrices in MapReduce architectures. IEEE International "
"Conference on Big Data, 2013. http://arxiv.org/abs/1301.1071"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:18 of
msgid "FSQR is a QR decomposition for fat and short matrix:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:19 of
msgid ""
"A = [A1, A2, A3, ...], A1 may be decomposed as A1 = Q1 * R1, for A = Q * "
"R, Q = Q1, R = [R1, R2, R3, ...] where A2 = Q1 * R2, A3 = Q1 * R3, ..."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:23 of
msgid ""
"* **q** (*Tensor of float or complex, optional*) -- A matrix with "
"orthonormal columns. When mode = 'complete' the   result is an "
"orthogonal/unitary matrix depending on whether or not   a is "
"real/complex. The determinant may be either +/- 1 in that   case. * **r**"
" (*Tensor of float or complex, optional*) -- The upper-triangular matrix."
msgstr ""
"* **q** (*Tensor of float or complex, optional*) -- 列向量正交的矩阵。当 "
"mode = 'complete' 时，结果是根据 a 是否为实数/复数决定的正交/酉矩阵。此时"
"行列式可能是 +/- 1。* **r** (*Tensor of float or complex, optional*) -- "
"上三角矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:23 of
msgid ""
"**q** (*Tensor of float or complex, optional*) -- A matrix with "
"orthonormal columns. When mode = 'complete' the result is an "
"orthogonal/unitary matrix depending on whether or not a is real/complex. "
"The determinant may be either +/- 1 in that case."
msgstr ""
"**q** (*Tensor of float or complex, optional*) -- 列向量正交的矩阵。当 "
"mode = 'complete' 时，结果是根据 a 是否为实数/复数决定的正交/酉矩阵。此时"
"行列式可能是 +/- 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:27 of
msgid ""
"**r** (*Tensor of float or complex, optional*) -- The upper-triangular "
"matrix."
msgstr "**r** (*Tensor of float or complex, optional*) -- 上三角矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:29 of
msgid "If factoring fails."
msgstr "如果分解失败。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:32 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.qr.qr:33 of
msgid ""
"For more information on the qr factorization, see for example: "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QR_factorization"
msgstr ""
"有关 QR 分解的更多信息，请参见：http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QR_"
"factorization"

